rows.label: tlk45340112_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there, Rex! This Divine Beast ship
catch your interest?

rows.label: tlk45340112_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It is the finest Divine Beast ship in all of
the Avaritia Trade Guild, after all.

rows.label: tlk45340112_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But as you can see, it's currently
undergoing maintenance. It won't
be setting sail for a while yet.

rows.label: tlk45340112_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If you want to see it in action,
try coming round another time.
